long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
YahooGPT(Yahoo Shopping:shopping.yahoo.jp) is a free AI-powered listing optimizer that helps Yahoo sellers optimize listing to improve Yahoo search ranking. 
With the help of YahooGPT, you will never need to search for Yahoo tips or templates for your listings. Just one click, you can get some better listing choices by ChatGPT OpenAI. 

ðŸš€ Features
â€’ Optimize title of Yahoo listing
â€’ Optimize description of Yahoo listing
â€’ Keywords finder and Keyword suggestion
â€’ Copy optimized listing content with one click
â€’ Export optimized listing content as .doc

ðŸš€ How to use
1. Optimize title
    a. Go to listing page of the product
    b. Open the YahooGPT and select Title Generator
    c. Search and pick keywords
    d. Click Generate Title button and get suggestion.
2. Optimize description
    a. Go to listing page of the product
    b. Open the YahooGPT and select Description Generator
    c. Search and select keywords, and set parameters.
    d. Click Generate Description and get suggestion.

ðŸš€ How it works
YahooGPT analyzes current product information such as title, description, keywords and uses ChatGPT to provide you with optimized listing content.
